<?php
$text = "PHP is awesome!";
echo substr($text, 0, 3) . "<br>";      // PHP
echo strpos($text, "awesome") . "<br>";// position
echo str_replace("awesome", "powerful", $text) . "<br>"; // replace
echo ucfirst("php") . "<br>";          // Php
echo ucwords("php is fun") . "<br>";   // Php Is Fun
?>

output:
PHP
7
PHP is powerful!
Php
Php Is Fun
